title: Side chair
medium: Walnut with walnut veneer on poplar seat rail
description: Slip seat. Plain cabroile legs ending in club feet; rounded back, vase-shaped splat.  Seat-rail, shaped, and back are veneered.  Legs joined by stretchers, the front one of turned baluster form.
